{"title":"小红帽脱险记  ４","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"４"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嗨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你真是小孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是小孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见识太少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世故不多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种整天睡觉的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没出息的坏主人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在该倒楣了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我难道还要做他的狗腿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让大家恨我骂我么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你对我从来就那么好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要帮助你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有我的道理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自有我的道理！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正说着说着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖可已经从山坡下面走上来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打着一把伞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一步的留心着走上山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口里还大声的喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这下你可逃不了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不把你吃掉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我永世也睡不着觉。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的声音那么高傲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么有自信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但一面又那么战战兢兢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步又停一停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他已经到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那黑色的魔手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在推开柴门了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"…………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小黄狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从屋角旁边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子窜了出来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛的一口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬住了老山妖的脚后跟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死死不放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越咬越深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哎呀，妈呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我中了钩镰枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我中了钩镰枪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的脚被钩住了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我痛得不得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的脚一定钩断了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬，嗬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走不得路了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嗬，嗬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跳不得舞了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大声的哭了起来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小黄狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高兴着他的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它想唱一个歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表示表示他的欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就张开了口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪汪汪的叫了几声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“呔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你呵，这小畜牲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我一向喂养着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对你不算错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怎么忘恩负义倒到了戈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反而来咬我？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反而来咬我？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你说对我很不错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可惜我的肚子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你管得并不多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为你守门，为你咬人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为你辛辛苦苦的工作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你可从不把我当人看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骂我，打我，又使唤我”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“笑话，笑话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这真是笑话！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你本来不是人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狗奴才忽然想做人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天底下哪有这种怪事情？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好，对你我有老办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天我带来两根骨头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根棍子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你选择哪一门？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“吓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老子现在脚跟痛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追不上你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侥你再活一晚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晚我一定要用你下饭！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歪着脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皱着眉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跛着脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步一拐的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下山去了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（第二节完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}